 * 4. Action items (actionable)
 * 5. Financial statements (financial.statement)
 * 6. Family communications (personal.family)
 *
 * These tests ensure the configuration system properly defines and validates these categories.
 * The tests validate configuration structure, required fields, Zod schema compliance,
 * and cross-reference integrity (domains, attributes).
